snippet.title: PS3 Longplay [071] Kingdom Hearts Final Mix HD (part 1 of 5)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: spazbo4

New Game - Easy Difficulty

Sorry but I really suck at this game on normal and proud difficulties so I played it on easy just to get through the story.

I try fighting Sephiroth, the Ice Giant, and the unknown optional bosses but I suck so bad I couldn't beat them so i am sorry I was unable to.

I play through most of the game with the default equipment until I got the Oblivion keyblade then I use that until I got the Lion Heart keyblade and I use that for the rest of the game.

http://www.youtube.com/spazbo3 -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
